       Target sources:

       auto extracted - target was extracted from SDC.

       auto computed - target was computed when balancing trees.

       auto scaled - target was computed by scaling the  primary  corner  skew
       target when balancing trees.

       explicit - target is explicitly set via target_max_trans property.

       pin  explicit  -  target  is  explicitly  set for this pin via pin_tar-
       get_max_trans property.

       liberty explicit - target is explicitly  set  via  max_transition  from
       liberty library.

